
=Bio=

"At the moment I study Sustainability Sciences at the Leuphana University Lüneburg, Germany. My interests are a new understanding of work, gender studies and the connection between sustainability and art. I'm also involved in networks such as "Recht auf Stadt" which claim the rights of the inhabitants of cities to create their own habitation."

